  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK199">
<l>poruṭīrnta poccāntuñ collār maruṭīrnta</l>
<l>mācaṟu kāṭci yavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those wise men who are without faults and are freed from ignorance will not even forgetfully speak things that profit not.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
